title: Everyone Living Under A Gun (New Release) Punk Rock Compilation
description:
In the vein of the punk rock compilations of the early 90\\\\\\\&#039;s comes Everyone Living Under A Gun. 20 Tracks from 20 Bands in like 50 minutes. It\\\\\\\&#039;s good time music for the people out there who like catchy pop tunes. Includes a cover of the hit, California Sun re-envisioned by San Joses very own, Shinobu.

The full album is available on pressed cd&#039;s with artwork by Mitch Clem (www.mitchclem.com) on The Political Party website at www.thepoliticalparty.net
